&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an IT Support Specialist who is passionate about delivering exceptional technical support and creating a best-in-class employee experience. You&#39;ll serve as the first point of contact for IT support, helping employees resolve technical issues quickly while ensuring they have the tools, access, and resources they need to be productive.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll support a modern cloud-based IT environment, assisting with user onboarding and offboarding, endpoint support, identity and access management, and administration of a broad portfolio of SaaS applications. This role reports to the Head of IT, but you will work closely with Security, People Operations, Clinical, and other business teams to provide reliable, secure, and friendly IT support across the organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;This is a remote position that can be located anywhere in the United States.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Will Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Deliver Exceptional Employee Support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide outstanding Tier 1 and Tier 2 technical support through our IT service desk, delivering a friendly, professional, and customer-first experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot hardware, software, identity, endpoint, and SaaS application issues from initial request through resolution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and prioritize support requests to ensure timely resolution and a positive employee experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate clearly with employees, keeping them informed throughout the support process and ensuring a positive support experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Escalate complex issues when appropriate while maintaining ownership and follow-through.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;User Lifecycle &amp;amp; Access Management&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver a seamless onboarding and offboarding experience by preparing user accounts, devices, software access, and ensuring employees are set up for success from day one through their last day.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provision, modify, and deprovision employee accounts across a variety of cloud applications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;

